[SN]TITLE[SN]
Borth Animalarium zoo in Ceredigion for sale

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Fancy a two-bedroom bungalow close to the Ceredigion coast? One is on the market, but it comes with snakes, monkeys, meerkats and 300 other animals.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The Animalarium in Borth is being sold by Jean and Alan Mumbray, who have owned it for 15 years.
